name: Help Dummy
description:
Runner Android game.

Your controle it by swipping left and right, it auto run as long as you let a finger on the screen.

You can take coins because we all love money and so you can show that you're better than your friends (we all know it's the only reason to try hard).

To finnish the level you will need to take the good clothes to pass all obstacles.

Have fun with it, maybe some new levels or ability will show up in the future.
